name: Beep
description: Beep is a meme coin that aims to be ubiquitous and fun, inspired by the everyday beeps we hear from devices all around us. With zero transaction taxes, a burned liquidity pool, and a renounced contract, Beep is designed to be a community-driven token on the Solana blockchain. It promises to empower communities, break down financial barriers, and provide a fun and engaging crypto experience. Join the movement and let Beep bring a bit of joy and simplicity to your crypto journey.
